[vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9344" align_center="aligncenter" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance][vc_column_text]

WE ARE CREATIVE

[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="2"][subtitle type="2" heading="3" subtitle_content="Our Story"][vc_column_text]EasyWeb is a premium design agency that focuses on quality, innovation, & speed. We utilized technology to bring results to grow our clients businesses. We pride ourselves in great work ethic, integrity, and end-results. Throughout the years EasyWeb has been able to create stunning, award winning designs in multiple verticals while allowing our clients to obtain an overall better web presence.  
Philosophy
Our company philosophy is to create the kind of website that most businesses want: easy to find, stylish and appealing, quick loading, mobile responsive and easy to buy from.  
Mission
We’ve designed our entire process and products around providing everything a small businesses needs when they’re starting out – ensuring that working with us is always a quick, easy and hassle-free experience. We give our clients full control of their website without a ridiculous price tag, and our friendly team offers their expertise even after your website is live.[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance][vc_single_image image="9343" img_size="full" alignment="right"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_bgcolor="#f6f8f9"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

DESIGN GROUP

With our in-house award winning designers, we recognize the fact that usability, functionality and visualization are three of the most important factors when designing interfaces or web sites. Using this strategy, we work with you to ensure that your messaging and marketing goals are realized with the designs we create. We will work with you and bring your idea to life.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="4/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

DEVELOPMENT GROUP

As a leading mobile application development company, EasyWeb has extensive experience in creating high performance, feature-packed native mobile applications for all the major mobile platforms including iOS, Android, BlackBerry OS and Windows Mobile. EasyWeb mobile app developers can create the right app that will meet your business, industry and/or vertical needs.

item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9223" align_center="aligncenter" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="3"][vc_column_text]

ONLINE MARKETING

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text]

Affordable Online Marketing

Our new fangled approach to advertising is directed creating and building deep love for your brand. We take a non-traditional approach to traditional media - breaking standards, methods and outdated practices of audience engagement

[/vc_column_text][distance][distance type="3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Email Marketing

Design engaging email marketing campaigns with simple drag-and-drop tools. Your design is guaranteed to look amazing in every inbox, on every device. We provide you with an unprecedented level of comfort and ease when creating and sending email campaigns.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9293" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Track Campaigns. Monitor Reports.

Tracking your email marketing campaign performance is easier with EasyWeb email marketing software. You can easily gain insight into how many recipients opened your email, how many emails bounced, unsubscribe rates and click through stats. EasyWeb offers a variety of ways to analyze and interpret your campaign performance with charts and data to help you improve your campaigns.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Send Your Campaign and Ensure Delivery.

Email campaigns can be sent at your convenience as we have it stored on the cloud, which means you can access it at anytime and anywhere using your desktop, tablet or iPhone. Schedule your campaign, or send it immediately. Check delivery in our reports and stats immediately. High delivery rates are guaranteed as we have feedback loops with all major internet service providers. [/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Social Media Marketing

A powerful tool of communication, social media allows companies to reach their customers where they are, while also characterizing their brands and expanding their customer base. If done correctly, social media marketing can also increase the efficacy of other marketing techniques – including SEO and SEM – by helping build natural links, and drive traffic, awareness, brand recognition and goodwill. If you have been struggling with social media strategy, management, or advertising we can help. [/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9294" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

What is Social Media Marketing?

Social media marketing, or SMM, is a form of internet marketing that implements various social media networks in order to achieve marketing communication and branding goals. Social media marketing primarily covers activities involving social sharing of content, videos, and images for marketing purposes, as well as paid social media advertising.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][vc_column_text]

How can we help you?

We are a sociable bunch and our new business comes primarily from recommendations & referrals from clients & friends who know how we work. We don’t think that salesmen should do all the talking for us and so we recommend that you speak directly to our clients to understand who we are and what we do. Our social media pricing is completely bespoke and is based on your current situation and your objectives. [/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Why do you need a social media management?

Your customers are on social media. Regardless of what industry your company is in, your customers are using social media on a daily basis. It is important that you keep them engaged and connected to your brand so that you’re always their first option. There are people searching for your company. If your company is offering a product or service, you can bet that there are people talking about it and looking for companies that provide it. Our social media management service will help your business to join the conversation and generate new leads. People are talking about your company on social media. You need to listen to what your customers are saying about your company on social media and respond to their concerns. Our social media management services focus on highlighting the positive aspects of what your company has to offer and respond sincerely to negative remarks. Companies deserve expert social media management. Most business owners and marketing managers do not have time to manage all of their social media channels. Each member of our firm received their certification in social media management and our agency can help you reach your marketing goals and a new customer base.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Mobile Marketing

Mobile Marketing is the latest technology that helps you attract more new customers --customers that spend more money, more frequently!!! We can help you launch a successful mobile marketing campaign to connect, communicate and keep your customers coming through the door again and again. [/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9295" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

What we do

Online marketing is considered to be one of the most popular methods of marketing. But the sheer number of mobile users dwarfs the potential of an online marketing campaign. As mobile phone users are more in number, the effectiveness and the eventual success of a mobile marketing campaign would be far stronger than what you could expect from an online marketing campaign, which still is a very popular method of marketing today[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Our mobile marketing services

  • Mobile Websites
  • SMS Marketing
  • Mobile Search Campaigns
  • HTML5 and CSS3
  • Mobile Commerce
  • 2D Barcodes/QR Codes
  • Mobile App Development
  • Mobile Marketing display campaigns

Search Engine Optimization

Is the process of affecting the visibility of a website or a web page in a search engine's unpaid results—often referred to as "natural," "organic," or "earned" results. In general, the earlier (or higher ranked on the search results page), and more frequently a site appears in the search results list, the more visitors it will receive from the search engine's users. SEO may target different kinds of search, including image search, local search, video search, academic search, news search and industry-specific vertical search engines.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9304" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="5"][maxtitle type="3" heading="1" maxtitle_content="Take Your Business to the next level"][vc_column_text]

Analyze a web site

We first analyze a web site, followed by a step-by-step plan to have the website communicate keywords more effectively to search engines. Our ultimate goal is to get our clients more visitors and higher conversion of sales and leads.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][vc_single_image image="9452" img_size="full"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="6/12"][distance type="2"][vc_single_image image="9457" img_size="full"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="6/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

On-Page & Off-Page Optimization

The search engine is a robot, not a human ... and therefore, you must follow our proven process to educate the robot so that it brings your website up when your potential customers are searching for specific business related keywords.[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][line][distance type="3"][maxtitle type="3" heading="1" maxtitle_content="HOW WE DO"][vc_column_text]

Digital Branding & Reputation Management

In business, reputation is everything. Thanks to social media and review sites like Yelp, you can build a great online reputation fast. There's just one problem: The Internet moves fast, and with a few missteps, you can hit rock bottom just as quickly as you rose to that coveted 5-star rating.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Our Expertise

We know that different businesses and individuals have distinct reputation management needs. Our staff researched and reviewed dozens of reputation management services, and came up with the ones we think are best for both businesses and individuals. We offer services to governments, and businesses, both small and large from a wide variety of industries and fields. Our exclusive solutions are focused not just on public perception, but also on our understanding of buying drivers for specific products. Public perception is vitally important, but our proprietary solutions are also focused on what drives sales for your products or services.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

What Makes Us Different.

If you currently have an online reputation management problem, our online reputation consultants can provide the tools you need to spot it and quietly remove it from search engines. If you’re lucky enough not to have a brand issue (yet), we’ll introduce you to reputation monitoring software that will help keep you abreast of what’s being said out there about your brand.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_height="452" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column el_class="aligncenter"][distance type="5"][distance][vc_column_text]

item.title: Social Media Marketing
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9334" align_center="aligncenter" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="3"][vc_column_text]

SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Social Media Marketing

A powerful tool of communication, social media allows companies to reach their customers where they are, while also characterizing their brands and expanding their customer base. If done correctly, social media marketing can also increase the efficacy of other marketing techniques – including SEO and SEM – by helping build natural links, and drive traffic, awareness, brand recognition and goodwill. If you have been struggling with social media strategy, management, or advertising we can help.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][maxtitle type="5" heading="1" maxtitle_content="Our Services"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="18" icon_title="Social Media Strategy Development" iconbox_content="We provide a range of high-value social media consultancy services through which we help you to achieve tangible results from their social media activities." icon_name="sl-puzzle"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="18" icon_title="Social Media Advertising Management" iconbox_content="Our social media advertising services are proven to accelerate growth. By advertising through social media, 100% of our clients have seen results." icon_name="sl-layers"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="2"][iconbox type="18" icon_title="Social Media Content Creation" iconbox_content="We provide a range of social media writing and posting services to help you directly or indirectly market your offerings through online social media." icon_name="sl-pencil"][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

What is Social Media Marketing?

Social media marketing, or SMM, is a form of internet marketing that implements various social media networks in order to achieve marketing communication and branding goals. Social media marketing primarily covers activities involving social sharing of content, videos, and images for marketing purposes, as well as paid social media advertising.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9412" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9413" img_size="full" alignment="center"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Why do you need a social media management?

 
Your customers are on social media.
Regardless of what industry your company is in, your customers are using social media on a daily basis. It is important that you keep them engaged and connected to your brand so that you’re always their first option.  
There are people searching for your company.
If your company is offering a product or service, you can bet that there are people talking about it and looking for companies that provide it. Our social media management service will help your business to join the conversation and generate new leads.  
People are talking about your company on social media.
You need to listen to what your customers are saying about your company on social media and respond to their concerns. Our social media management services focus on highlighting the positive aspects of what your company has to offer and respond sincerely to negative remarks.  
Companies deserve expert social media management.
Most business owners and marketing managers do not have time to manage all of their social media channels. Each member of our firm received their certification in social media management and our agency can help you reach your marketing goals and a new customer base.[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="3"][maxtitle type="5" heading="1" maxtitle_content="Our Process"][distance][our_process process_item="%5B%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22%3Cstrong%3EStrategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Development%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-cubes%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22%3Cstrong%3EAdvertising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Management%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-bullhorn%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Management%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-male%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22%3Cstrong%3EEffective%20Content%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Creation%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-pencil%22%7D%2C%7B%22process_title%22%3A%22%3Cstrong%3EMeasurement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26%20Reporting%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-area-chart%22%7D%5D"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9196" align_center="aligncenter" blox_padding_bottom="40" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column width="1/6"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][distance type="5"][distance type="2"][vc_column_text css_animation="appear"]

How can we help you?

We are a sociable bunch and our new business comes primarily from recommendations & referrals from clients & friends who know how we work. We don’t think that salesmen should do all the talking for us and so we recommend that you speak directly to our clients to understand who we are and what we do. Our social media pricing is completely bespoke and is based on your current situation and your objectives.

item.content:encoded:
[vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9340" align_center="aligncenter" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="3"][vc_column_text]

PAY PER CLICK

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="1/4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

What is Pay Per Click?

PPC stands for pay-per-click, a model of internet marketing in which advertisers pay a fee each time one of their ads is clicked. Essentially, it’s a way of buying visits to your site, rather than attempting to “earn” those visits organically. Search engine advertising is one of the most popular forms of PPC. It allows advertisers to bid for ad placement in a search engine's sponsored links when someone searches on a keyword that is related to their business offering.

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

PPC Management

Platforms such as Google AdWords and Bing Ads are important to your business. With our pay-per-click marketing (PPC) expertise, we can help take your accounts to the next level. We customize strategy and reporting tailored to your needs. We provide the support and guidance you require to accomplish your goal, be it maximizing return on investment, increasing leads, or driving brand awareness.[/vc_column_text][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="9419" img_size="full"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_padding_top="70" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column][maxtitle type="3" maxtitle_content="Our Pay Per Click Services"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" blox_padding_top="1" blox_padding_bottom="15" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="PPC Audits" iconbox_content="Our PPC Audit process starts from understanding audit objective, coverage and leading to data analysis. " icon_name="sl-eyeglass"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Bing Advertising" iconbox_content="Our in-house Bing ads agency team has the training and expertise you need to make the most of Bing’s popular PPC platform. " icon_name="fa-windows"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="Social Advertising" iconbox_content="EasySeo can help you with paid social campaigns that can drive your target audience toward much targeted desired actions. " icon_name="sl-rocket"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Display Advertising" iconbox_content="Your display ads will be targeting an audience that has already indicated an interest in your service or product. " icon_name="fa-bullhorn"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox icon_title="Google AdWords" iconbox_content=" Hiring us gives you the benefit of a full-time AdWords expert without the extra cost of hiring another full-time employee." icon_name="fa-google"][distance type="2"][iconbox icon_title="Remarketing & Retargeting" iconbox_content="Improve ROI and increase conversions by marketing to people who have all ready visited your website. " icon_name="sl-refresh"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="4"][vc_single_image image="9420" img_size="full"][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Brief process of our pay per click campaign:

Our pay-per-click (PPC) management service includes the following components:
  • PPC search campaign strategy
  • Keyword research and selection
  • Ad creative development
  • Campaign set-up
  • Bid management and ROI tracking
  • Landing page optimization and development
  • Campaign management and analysis
[/vc_column_text][distance type="3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9107" blox_padding_top="15" blox_padding_bottom="10" blox_dark="true" blox_bgcolor="#00c2e5" parallax_speed="7" row_pattern="max-pat2"][vc_column][distance type="3"][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation="appear"]

Deliverables

We report monthly on your campaign’s success regarding keyword choice and text choice, and we create a rank report so you know where you rank organically for the keywords you pay for. Additionally, after you review the report, we’ll book a one hour call with the members of your team to explain your campaign’s progress, direction, and answer any questions you may have.

[vc_row row_type="3" blox_image="9450" align_center="aligncenter" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true" parallax_speed="7"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][distance type="3"][vc_column_text]

MOBILE MARKETING

[/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="2" page_title="page-title-x" blox_padding_top="50" blox_padding_bottom="50" blox_bgcolor="#f7f7f7"][vc_column width="7/12"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

Mobile Marketing

Mobile Marketing is the latest technology that helps you attract more new customers --customers that spend more money, more frequently!!! We can help you launch a successful mobile marketing campaign to connect, communicate and keep your customers coming through the door again and again. [/vc_column_text][distance type="5"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="9447" img_size="full" alignment="right" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="2"][maxtitle type="3" maxtitle_content="Our Services"][distance][vc_column_text]

Online marketing is considered to be one of the most popular methods of marketing. But the sheer number of mobile users dwarfs the potential of an online marketing campaign. As mobile phone users are more in number, the effectiveness and the eventual success of a mobile marketing campaign would be far stronger than what you could expect from an online marketing campaign, which still is a very popular method of marketing today.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox type="8" icon_title="Mobile App Development" iconbox_content="We help you create a seamless experience for your web applications on handheld devices using responsive design, HTML5 and CSS3." icon_name="sl-screen-tablet"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][distance type="3"][iconbox type="8" icon_title="Mobile Websites services" iconbox_content="As a full-service agency, we offer a range of mobile web services.
